<p class="wikiPara">
Hibernate ORM 4.2.2.Final was just released. The full changelog can be viewed <a href="https://hibernate.atlassian.net/secure/ReleaseNote.jspa?projectId=10031&amp;version=13351" target="" class="regularLink">here</a>
</p>

<p class="wikiPara">
In addition to numerous bug fixes, notable changes include:
</p>

<ul class="wikiUnorderedList">
<li class="wikiUnorderedListItem"> <a href="https://hibernate.atlassian.net/browse/HHH-8217" target="" class="regularLink">HHH-8217</a> reworked <a href="https://hibernate.atlassian.net/browse/HHH-1904" target="" class="regularLink">HHH-1904</a> and made generated constraint names short and non-random</li>
<li class="wikiUnorderedListItem"> <a href="https://hibernate.atlassian.net/browse/HHH-7944" target="" class="regularLink">HHH-7944</a> added OSGi support to Envers</li>
<li class="wikiUnorderedListItem"> <a href="https://hibernate.atlassian.net/browse/HHH-7995" target="" class="regularLink">HHH-7995</a> supports the use of OSGi services to register Hibernate extension points</li>
</ul>

